      <title>InZOI: Esports Career Guide</title>
      <link>https://gamerant.com/inzoi-esports-career-guide-become-pro-player/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<div class="content-block-regular">
 <p>
  Just like other life simulation games, there are many careers in
  <em>
   <strong>
    InZOI
   </strong>
   ,
  </em>
  and one of the most unique and exciting for players is an esports career. This job allows Zois to
  <strong>
   become pro gamers
  </strong>
  , starting out as amateurs and eventually becoming world-renowned superstars.
 </p>
 <!-- Not injecting Ads due to No-Ads mode. -->
 <p>
  Unfortunately, at Early Access launch, this
  <em>
   InZOI
  </em>
  career is a
  <strong>
   'rabbit hole' job
  </strong>
  , meaning that the Zoi will get in a taxi to leave for work, and players
  <strong>
   won't be able to control them
  </strong>
  until the shift is over. Down the line, this will hopefully be updated to become an active job, similar to the firefighter career, for example.
 </p>
 <!-- Not injecting Ads due to No-Ads mode. -->
 <h2 id="best-traits-amp-setup-for-the-esports-career-in-inzoi">
  Best Traits &amp; Setup For The Esports Career In InZOI
 </h2>
 <div class="body-img landscape">
  <div class="responsive-img image-expandable img-article-item" data-img-caption='""' data-img-url="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-go-getter-trait.jpg" data-modal-container-id="single-image-modal-container" data-modal-id="single-image-modal">
   <figure>
    <picture>
     <source data-srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-go-getter-trait.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=825&amp;dpr=2" media="(min-width: 1024px)" srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-go-getter-trait.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=825&amp;dpr=2"/>
     <source data-srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-go-getter-trait.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=825&amp;dpr=2" media="(min-width: 768px)" srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-go-getter-trait.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=825&amp;dpr=2"/>
     <source data-srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-go-getter-trait.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=800&amp;dpr=2" media="(min-width: 481px)" srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-go-getter-trait.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=800&amp;dpr=2"/>
     <source data-srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-go-getter-trait.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=500&amp;dpr=2" media="(min-width: 0px)" srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-go-getter-trait.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=500&amp;dpr=2"/>
     <img alt="InZOI Go-Getter Trait" data-img-url="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-go-getter-trait.jpg" decoding="async" height="1080" loading="lazy" src="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-go-getter-trait.jpg" style="display:block;height:auto;max-width:100%;" width="1920"/>
    </picture>
   </figure>
  </div>
 </div>
 <p>
  For the best chance of succeeding as an esports player in
  <em>
   InZOI
  </em>
  , players can give their Zois certain Traits and Preferences, and perhaps most importantly,
  <strong>
   work on the programming skill
  </strong>
  .
 </p>
 <h3 id="best-traits-for-the-esports-career">
  Best Traits For The Esports Career
 </h3>
 <ul>
  <li>
   Go-Getter
  </li>
  <li>
   Perfectionist
  </li>
  <li>
   Leader
  </li>
 </ul>
 <h3 id="best-preferences-for-the-esports-career">
  Best Preferences For The Esports Career
 </h3>
 <ul>
  <li>
   Gaming
  </li>
  <li>
   Self-Help Books
  </li>
  <li>
   Coffee
  </li>
 </ul>
 <h3 id="how-to-level-up-the-programming-skill">
  How To Level Up The Programming Skill
 </h3>
 <p>
  Zois will need to
  <strong>
   work on programming in their spare time
  </strong>
  , as this will make them
  <strong>
   better gamers
  </strong>
  . This is one advantage of starting as an adolescent or teenager, as they can reach the
  <strong>
   maximum level of 10 in programming
  </strong>
  before starting their esports career.
 </p>
 <ul>
  <li>
   Gaming at a PC, the PC Cafe (Plesio Gaming Cafe), or on a handheld device.
  </li>
  <li>
   Work on coding on a home PC. This includes plugins, mods, games, and apps.
  </li>
  <li>
   Read books on programming.
  </li>
  <li>
   During school, click on the briefcase next to your Zoi in the top right. There's an option to slip away to the gaming cafe during breaks.
  </li>
  <li>
   Talk about gaming strategies with friends.
  </li>
 </ul>
 <h2 id="requirements-for-becoming-an-esports-player-in-inzoi">
  Requirements For Becoming An Esports Player In InZOI
 </h2>
 <div class="body-img landscape">
  <div class="responsive-img image-expandable img-article-item" data-img-caption='""' data-img-url="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-gamer-setup.jpg" data-modal-container-id="single-image-modal-container" data-modal-id="single-image-modal">
   <figure>
    <picture>
     <source data-srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-gamer-setup.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=825&amp;dpr=2" media="(min-width: 1024px)" srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-gamer-setup.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=825&amp;dpr=2"/>
     <source data-srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-gamer-setup.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=825&amp;dpr=2" media="(min-width: 768px)" srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-gamer-setup.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=825&amp;dpr=2"/>
     <source data-srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-gamer-setup.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=800&amp;dpr=2" media="(min-width: 481px)" srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-gamer-setup.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=800&amp;dpr=2"/>
     <source data-srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-gamer-setup.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=500&amp;dpr=2" media="(min-width: 0px)" srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-gamer-setup.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=500&amp;dpr=2"/>
     <img alt="InZOI Gamer Setup" data-img-url="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-gamer-setup.jpg" decoding="async" height="1080" loading="lazy" src="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-gamer-setup.jpg" style="display:block;height:auto;max-width:100%;" width="1920"/>
    </picture>
   </figure>
  </div>
 </div>
 <p>
  Not everyone can become an esports player in
  <em>
   InZOI
  </em>
  ​​​. Here are
  <strong>
   some requirements:
  </strong>
 </p>
 <ul>
  <li>
   <strong>
    Live in Dowon
   </strong>
   , as this is an exclusive career in this city.
  </li>
  <li>
   Be a young adult, adult, or middle-aged. Teenagers are too young to work.
  </li>
  <li>
   Don't have another job. Being an esports player is a full-time career.
  </li>
 </ul>
 <section class="emaki-custom-block emaki-custom-tip" data-nosnippet="">
  <div class="emaki-custom tip" id="custom_block_18">
   <div class="custom_block-content tip">
    <p>
     For immersion and a fun playthrough, players could create 5 Zois who all become esports players and live in a gaming house together like many real teams do.
    </p>
   </div>
  </div>
 </section>
 <div class="ad-even">
  <!-- Not injecting Ads due to No-Ads mode. -->
 </div>
 <h2 id="how-to-become-a-pro-esports-player-in-inzoi">
  How To Become A Pro Esports Player In InZOI
 </h2>
 <div class="body-img landscape">
  <div class="responsive-img image-expandable img-article-item" data-img-caption='""' data-img-url="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-esports-career-progress.jpg" data-modal-container-id="single-image-modal-container" data-modal-id="single-image-modal">
   <figure>
    <picture>
     <source data-srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-esports-career-progress.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=825&amp;dpr=2" media="(min-width: 1024px)" srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-esports-career-progress.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=825&amp;dpr=2"/>
     <source data-srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-esports-career-progress.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=825&amp;dpr=2" media="(min-width: 768px)" srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-esports-career-progress.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=825&amp;dpr=2"/>
     <source data-srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-esports-career-progress.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=800&amp;dpr=2" media="(min-width: 481px)" srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-esports-career-progress.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=800&amp;dpr=2"/>
     <source data-srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-esports-career-progress.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=500&amp;dpr=2" media="(min-width: 0px)" srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-esports-career-progress.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=500&amp;dpr=2"/>
     <img alt="InZOI Esports Career Progress" data-img-url="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-esports-career-progress.jpg" decoding="async" height="1080" loading="lazy" src="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-esports-career-progress.jpg" style="display:block;height:auto;max-width:100%;" width="1920"/>
    </picture>
   </figure>
  </div>
 </div>
 <p>
  Once Zois become a young adult, or decide to leave another job, they can press
  <strong>
   P to bring up the phone
  </strong>
  and then navigate to the Careers app. Click on DG Esports and apply to be an amateur gamer.
 </p>
 <p>
  After being accepted, Zois will have a new schedule for the week, with
  <strong>
   three days being spent at work
  </strong>
  . All you need to do is make sure your Zoi is available at these times,
  <strong>
   well-rested
  </strong>
  , and
  <strong>
   fed
  </strong>
  . If you are controlling them directly when the time arrives, a
  <strong>
   pop-up will appear
  </strong>
  , so make sure to select the go to work option.
 </p>
 <h3 id="what-to-do-at-work-as-an-esports-player">
  What To Do At Work As An Esports Player
 </h3>
 <div class="body-img landscape">
  <div class="responsive-img image-expandable img-article-item" data-img-caption='""' data-img-url="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-esports-career-event.jpg" data-modal-container-id="single-image-modal-container" data-modal-id="single-image-modal">
   <figure>
    <picture>
     <source data-srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-esports-career-event.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=825&amp;dpr=2" media="(min-width: 1024px)" srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-esports-career-event.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=825&amp;dpr=2"/>
     <source data-srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-esports-career-event.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=825&amp;dpr=2" media="(min-width: 768px)" srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-esports-career-event.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=825&amp;dpr=2"/>
     <source data-srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-esports-career-event.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=800&amp;dpr=2" media="(min-width: 481px)" srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-esports-career-event.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=800&amp;dpr=2"/>
     <source data-srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-esports-career-event.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=500&amp;dpr=2" media="(min-width: 0px)" srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-esports-career-event.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=500&amp;dpr=2"/>
     <img alt="InZOI Esports Career Event" data-img-url="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-esports-career-event.jpg" decoding="async" height="1080" loading="lazy" src="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-esports-career-event.jpg" style="display:block;height:auto;max-width:100%;" width="1920"/>
    </picture>
   </figure>
  </div>
 </div>
 <p>
  For the time being, the esports career unfortunately does not have much interaction, with the Zoi
  <strong>
   getting in a taxi and disappearing for the day
  </strong>
  . Hopefully, at a later date during Early Access, this will become an active job.
 </p>
 <p>
  In the
  <strong>
   top right
  </strong>
  , players can click on a
  <strong>
   briefcase icon next to their Zoi and choose some options
  </strong>
  , but other than the 'Leave Early' decision, it doesn't appear as though these have an impact. The other options are:
 </p>
 <ul>
  <li>
   Participate in Guild Raid
  </li>
  <li>
   Start Gaming Live Stream
  </li>
  <li>
   Check Game Patch Notes
  </li>
  <li>
   Get In-Game Achievement
  </li>
 </ul>
 <p>
  There will be some
  <strong>
   important decisions
  </strong>
  , however, which
  <strong>
   pop up during the working day
  </strong>
  with different outcomes. For example, a Zoi might find themselves 1 v 5 in a mostly lost game. The options are whether they should give up and save some mental energy, or fight it out for the small chance of victory?
 </p>
 <section class="emaki-custom-block emaki-custom-note" data-nosnippet="">
  <div class="emaki-custom note" id="custom_block_29">
   <div class="custom_block-content note">
    <p>
     You only have 30 seconds to read these events and select an option.
    </p>
   </div>
  </div>
 </section>
 <h3 id="how-to-get-promoted-as-an-esports-player">
  How To Get Promoted As An Esports Player
 </h3>
 <div class="body-img landscape">
  <div class="responsive-img image-expandable img-article-item" data-img-caption='""' data-img-url="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-dg-esports-job-promotion.jpg" data-modal-container-id="single-image-modal-container" data-modal-id="single-image-modal">
   <figure>
    <picture>
     <source data-srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-dg-esports-job-promotion.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=825&amp;dpr=2" media="(min-width: 1024px)" srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-dg-esports-job-promotion.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=825&amp;dpr=2"/>
     <source data-srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-dg-esports-job-promotion.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=825&amp;dpr=2" media="(min-width: 768px)" srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-dg-esports-job-promotion.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=825&amp;dpr=2"/>
     <source data-srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-dg-esports-job-promotion.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=800&amp;dpr=2" media="(min-width: 481px)" srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-dg-esports-job-promotion.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=800&amp;dpr=2"/>
     <source data-srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-dg-esports-job-promotion.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=500&amp;dpr=2" media="(min-width: 0px)" srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-dg-esports-job-promotion.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=500&amp;dpr=2"/>
     <img alt="InZOI DG Esports Job Promotion" data-img-url="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-dg-esports-job-promotion.jpg" decoding="async" height="1080" loading="lazy" src="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/inzoi-dg-esports-job-promotion.jpg" style="display:block;height:auto;max-width:100%;" width="1920"/>
    </picture>
   </figure>
  </div>
 </div>
 <p>
  There are currently
  <strong>
   three levels in
   <em>
    InZOI's
   </em>
   esports career:
  </strong>
 </p>
 <ul>
  <li>
   Amateur Gamer: 264 Meows
  </li>
  <li>
   Pro Gamer: 864 Meows
  </li>
  <li>
   Legendary Gamer: 1998 Meows
  </li>
 </ul>
 <p>
  To
  <strong>
   advance
  </strong>
  and earn more money, Zois will want to make sure they
  <strong>
   don't miss any days or leave work early
  </strong>
  . To go from an Amateur Gamer to a Pro Gamer, Zois will need to work for
  <strong>
   6 full days
  </strong>
  . Players can check their progress in the careers app.
 </p>
 <p>
  <strong>
   After reaching 100% progress
  </strong>
  , some time will pass, and
  <strong>
   within a few days
  </strong>
  , Zois should get a pop-up and
  <strong>
   text message informing them of their promotion
  </strong>
  . For now, not much changes other than them
  <strong>
   earning more money
  </strong>
  . The progress toward becoming a Legendary Gamer appears to be bugged or not implemented at the moment.
 </p>
</div>]]></description>
