      <title>Assassin's Creed Shadows: Should You Be Patient With Tokugawa? (Wolves And Foxes Quest)</title>
      <link>https://gamerant.com/assassins-creed-shadows-should-you-be-patient-with-tokugawa-wolves-and-foxes/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<div class="content-block-regular">
 <p>
  Wolves and Foxes is one of the first quests from Naoe's questline in
  <em>
   <strong>
    Assassin's Creed Shadows
   </strong>
  </em>
  , where players must help an Igan battalion fight off Mitsuhide's battalion. Once the dust settled, Tokugawa extended his gratitude to Yasuke and Naoe for lending a helping hand in the battle. After the initial conversation, you'll get a choice to either respond as Naoe, that they should be swift in their action, or Yasuke, that they should be patient. Let's check out both of the outcomes of this encounter.
 </p>
 <!-- Not injecting Ads due to No-Ads mode. -->
 <!-- Not injecting Ads due to No-Ads mode. -->
 <h2 id="how-to-start-the-wolves-and-foxes-quest-in-ac-shadows">
  How to Start the Wolves and Foxes Quest in AC Shadows
 </h2>
 <div class="valnet-gallery">
  <div class="article__gallery type-gallery" data-article-gallery="article-gallery-modal-1-1662907026" data-gallery-id="main-carousel-1-1662907026" data-gallery-lightbox="gallery-modal-1-1662907026" data-gallery-thumbnail-id="gallery-thumbnails-1-1662907026" data-gallery-thumbnail-img-class="gallery-thumbnails-1-1662907026-img" id="article-gallery-1-1662907026">
  </div>
  <div class="gallery-lightbox" id="gallery-modal-1-1662907026" style="display: none">
   <button class="lightbox__exit-btn icon i-close">
    <span class="txt">
     Close
    </span>
   </button>
   <div class="lightbox">
    <div class="lightbox__swipper" id="swipper-1">
     <div class="swiper-wrapper" id="gallery-modal-1-slides-container-1563527422">
     </div>
     <div class="swiper-button-next icon i-arrow-1">
     </div>
     <div class="swiper-button-prev icon i-arrow-1">
     </div>
    </div>
   </div>
  </div>
 </div>
 <p>
  After completing the Before the Fall quest in
  <em>
   Assassin's Creed Shadows
  </em>
  , players will
  <strong>
   unlock the Wolves and Foxes quest
  </strong>
  from Naoe's questline. The quest requires Naoe to travel to the Little Leaf Glade area of the Yamashiro province to meet up with Tokugawa Ieyasu and defend Igan soldiers from Mitsuhide's battalion.
 </p>
 <p>
  When you arrive at the location, you'll witness dozens of soldiers in the leaf glade battling Igan warriors. The first objective is to
  <strong>
   eliminate all the soldiers
  </strong>
  before talking to Tokugawa. Once all of Mitsuhide's soldiers are eliminated, players will need to approach Tokugawa and talk to him.
 </p>
 <h2 id="should-you-be-patient-with-tokugawa">
  Should You Be Patient With Tokugawa?
 </h2>
 <div class="body-img landscape">
  <div class="responsive-img image-expandable img-article-item" data-img-caption='""' data-img-url="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/should-you-be-patient-with-tokugawa-wolves-and-foxes-quest-ac-shadows.jpg" data-modal-container-id="single-image-modal-container" data-modal-id="single-image-modal">
   <figure>
    <picture>
     <source data-srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/should-you-be-patient-with-tokugawa-wolves-and-foxes-quest-ac-shadows.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=825&amp;dpr=2" media="(min-width: 1024px)" srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/should-you-be-patient-with-tokugawa-wolves-and-foxes-quest-ac-shadows.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=825&amp;dpr=2"/>
     <source data-srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/should-you-be-patient-with-tokugawa-wolves-and-foxes-quest-ac-shadows.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=825&amp;dpr=2" media="(min-width: 768px)" srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/should-you-be-patient-with-tokugawa-wolves-and-foxes-quest-ac-shadows.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=825&amp;dpr=2"/>
     <source data-srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/should-you-be-patient-with-tokugawa-wolves-and-foxes-quest-ac-shadows.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=800&amp;dpr=2" media="(min-width: 481px)" srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/should-you-be-patient-with-tokugawa-wolves-and-foxes-quest-ac-shadows.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=800&amp;dpr=2"/>
     <source data-srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/should-you-be-patient-with-tokugawa-wolves-and-foxes-quest-ac-shadows.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=500&amp;dpr=2" media="(min-width: 0px)" srcset="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/should-you-be-patient-with-tokugawa-wolves-and-foxes-quest-ac-shadows.jpg?q=49&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=500&amp;dpr=2"/>
     <img alt="Should You Be Patient With Tokugawa Wolves and Foxes quest AC Shadows" data-img-url="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/should-you-be-patient-with-tokugawa-wolves-and-foxes-quest-ac-shadows.jpg" decoding="async" height="1100" loading="lazy" src="https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/should-you-be-patient-with-tokugawa-wolves-and-foxes-quest-ac-shadows.jpg" style="display:block;height:auto;max-width:100%;" width="2200"/>
    </picture>
   </figure>
  </div>
 </div>
 <p>
  Tokugawa will be thankful for Naoe and Yasuke's intervention in the battle that led to their victory. Soon after, Naoe learns that Tokugawa is opting to retreat from Mitsuhide's rule with the help of Hattori Hanzo and will patiently wait for the right moment to strike. After this,
  <strong>
   players will get the dialog choice
  </strong>
  to either respond with "We will be patient" by Yasuke or "Patience will not stop Mitsuhide" by Naoe.
 </p>
 <p>
  Here's the difference between both responses in
  <em>
   Assassin's Creed Shadows
  </em>
  ' Wolves and Foxes quest.
 </p>
 <h3 id="choosing-yasuke-39-s-response-quot-we-will-be-patient-quot">
  Choosing Yasuke's Response "We Will Be Patient"
 </h3>
 <p>
  Yasuke will respond with his mother's saying that "
  <strong>
   Haste leads to waste
  </strong>
  ," which Tokugawa will agree with. He'll further explain his reasoning behind the plan and stress the fact that the aim is peace, and they'll achieve it.
 </p>
 <h3 id="choosing-naoe-39-s-response-quot-patience-will-not-stop-mitsuhide-quot">
